description: Melvin Theuma was due to give evidence in court and police say his wounds were self-inflicted.
title: Daphne Caruana Galizia murder: Middleman critically wounded
title_page: Daphne Caruana Galizia murder: Middleman critically wounded - BBC News
maintext: The self-confessed middleman has already given evidence, saying he was paid by the suspect to hire three men accused of carrying out the attack. He has also said that he lives in fear of his life.
